overview: Kang Mus retired as a boss thug. Now Kang Mus wants to start a new business, selling kicimpring. Esih supports the goodwill of Kang Mus, now they start to live sparingly and reduce spending to venture capital. The retirement of Kang Mus makes Bobi and Baba again want to be a penodong, because there is now no more blocking.
title: Preman Pensiun: Sang Juara
